Robin,

You're getting some good book ideas, but do you know about the NE
Unschooling conference? It will be in Peabody MA this coming May, run
by Kathryn Baptista. Great chance to meet real life unschoolers and
hear from a variety of people.

http://www.northeastunschoolingconference.com/

Ren
